---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
import Button from '../Button.astro';
---
<SectionWrapper id="problem" theme="light">
  <!-- Section label -->
  <p class="section-label section-label--light">// 02 PROBLEM IDENTIFIED</p>

  <!-- Headline -->
  <h2 class="problem-headline">Your business is missing one thing.</h2>

  <!-- Body copy -->
  <div class="problem-body">
    <p>
      Every small business runs on three things: the message you put in front of
      strangers, the tools you use to do your work, and the website that holds it
      all together. Most business owners treat these as three separate problems.
      They're not. They're three layers of the same missing system.
    </p>

    <p>
      Maybe you've been in business for years. Maybe you're just starting out.
      Either way, if your message, your site, and your tools weren't built to
      work together, you don't have an operating system for your business. You
      have parts.
    </p>

    <p>
      Parts don't convert. Parts don't scale. And you end up being the glue that
      holds them all together, manually, every day.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Philosophical statement -->
  <blockquote class="problem-philosophy" data-animate>
    <p>Good work deserves to be found.</p>
    <p>Bad marketing shouldn't be a tax on good work.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <!-- ERR nodes -->
  <ul class="err-stack" data-animate>
    <li class="err-node">
      <div class="err-status">
        <span class="err-badge">[ERR]</span>
        <span class="err-label">YOUR MESSAGE</span>
      </div>
      <p class="err-desc">
        Strangers visit your site and can't figure out what you do. They leave.
        Someone with a worse product but a clearer message gets the call.
      </p>
      <p class="err-cite">
        "Your site forms a first impression in 50ms. Before anyone reads a word."
      </p>
      <p class="err-source">// Lindgaard, Behavioural &amp; IT, 2006</p>
    </li>

    <li class="err-node">
      <div class="err-status">
        <span class="err-badge">[ERR]</span>
        <span class="err-label">YOUR SITE</span>
      </div>
      <p class="err-desc">
        You send someone to your website and feel that quiet dread: will this
        make me look smaller than I actually am?
      </p>
      <p class="err-cite">
        "Only 1 in 5 small business owners believe their marketing is actually working."
      </p>
      <p class="err-source">// Constant Contact / Ascend2, 2025</p>
    </li>

    <li class="err-node">
      <div class="err-status">
        <span class="err-badge">[ERR]</span>
        <span class="err-label">YOUR TOOLS</span>
      </div>
      <p class="err-desc">
        You bought software one tool at a time. Each one solved a specific
        problem. Now you're the thing that connects them. That wasn't the plan.
      </p>
      <p class="err-cite">
        "The average small business owner spends ~1.5 hours per day on tool switching alone."
      </p>
      <p class="err-source">// Slack / Salesforce Productivity Survey, 2024</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="problem-cta">
    <Button variant="primary" href="/diagnostic">[GET YOUR FREE DIAGNOSTIC &gt;]</Button>
    <p class="problem-cta-note">// Five minutes tells you exactly which layer is broken.</p>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Headline - Geist Sans */
  .problem-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-4);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  /* Body copy */
  .problem-body {
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .problem-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .problem-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Philosophical blockquote */
  .problem-philosophy {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
  }

  .problem-philosophy p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .problem-philosophy p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ERR stack */
  .err-stack {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .err-node {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--bg-light);
  }

  /* ERR status line */
  .err-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .err-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--error);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .err-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ERR description */
  .err-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  /* ERR citation */
  .err-cite {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .err-source {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
  }

  /* CTA area */
  .problem-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .problem-cta-note {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-3);
    }

    .problem-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .problem-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }
  }
</style>
